insights.summary: ChatGPTis your AI chatbot for everyday use Weve trained a model calledChatGPTwhich interacts in a conversational way The dialogue format makes it possible forChatGPTto answer followup questions, admit its mistakes, challenge incorrect premises, and reject inappropriate requests ChatGPTis a free app that lets you create and transform images, have conversations, and get advice from OpenAIs latest models ChatGPTis a generative artificial intelligence chatbot developed by OpenAI and released in November 2022
